    <name>Key Idea: Experiential learning builds learner agency and self-advocacy skills.</name>
    <intro></intro>
    <introformat>1</introformat>
    <content>&lt;p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;&lt;img src="@@PLUGINFILE@@/Key%20Idea.png" alt="" width="140" height="136" role="presentation" class="img-responsive atto_image_button_middle"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;Experiential learning&amp;nbsp; - or "learning by doing" - gives adult learners a chance to build agency&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;by creating learning experiences where they can&amp;nbsp;exercise personal choice and follow innate&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;curiosity. Experiential learning can also&amp;nbsp;build self-advocacy skills, if educators allow learners&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;to construct learning experiences that meet their learning needs. To make the learning stick,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;and ensure learners develop self-advocacy skills&amp;nbsp;educators should engage adult learners in&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;deliberate reflection and purposeful connection-making, post-experience&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="$@PAGEVIEWBYID*9955@$" target="_blank"&gt;(Paradiz et al., 2018 and Decker et al., 2015)&lt;/a&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;&lt;img src="@@PLUGINFILE@@/Divider%20Wave%20%281%29.png" alt="" width="1920" height="195" role="presentation" class="img-responsive atto_image_button_text-bottom"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</content>
